OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHusband of ex-Post Office  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fboss advised on IT 'bug'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Post Office changed how it         
OL,6, described problems with its Horizon IT 
OL,7, system based on a suggestion by the    
OL,8, husband of former boss, Paula Vennells.
OL,10,FThe inquiry into the scandal has       
OL,11,Frevealed that following advice from    
OL,12,FJohn Vennells, the Post Office stopped 
OL,13,Freferring to "bugs", and instead called
OL,14,Fthem "anomalies and exceptions".       
OL,16,FSenior executives felt that this       
OL,17,Flanguage was "less emotive".           
OL,19,FBut a lawyer for the inquiry branded   
OL,20,Fthe move as "absolutely Orwellian".    
